  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build on rooftops</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/c25554fe2c84584ff83d62873d4e89e3.poster.avif?t=1743230903\" width=598 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/c25554fe2c84584ff83d62873d4e89e3.webm?t=1743230903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/c25554fe2c84584ff83d62873d4e89e3.mp4?t=1743230903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Construct buildings on <strong>rooftops</strong> to save space and gain strategic advantages, like shooting over walls to defend against threats, making it easier to take down zombies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless zombie hordes push you to the limit.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/377f6c4137424d80b5f6e12c94835126.poster.avif?t=1743230903\" width=598 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/377f6c4137424d80b5f6e12c94835126.webm?t=1743230903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/377f6c4137424d80b5f6e12c94835126.mp4?t=1743230903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The zombie horde never stops. They are too many. <strong>Research, develop advanced technology, and train survivors</strong> to combat the ever-growing and evolving undead threat. Adapt or be overrun.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grow, manage, and protect your settlement</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/8bfc39e01c8f2aa0465a48df26dc5bd3.poster.avif?t=1743230903\" width=598 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/8bfc39e01c8f2aa0465a48df26dc5bd3.webm?t=1743230903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/8bfc39e01c8f2aa0465a48df26dc5bd3.mp4?t=1743230903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Create a secure haven where survivors can <strong>eat, sleep, and recover</strong>. Establish a steady supply of food and resources, and build an efficient crafting chain to support your frontline fighters. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build on rooftops</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/c25554fe2c84584ff83d62873d4e89e3.poster.avif?t=1743230903\" width=598 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/c25554fe2c84584ff83d62873d4e89e3.webm?t=1743230903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/c25554fe2c84584ff83d62873d4e89e3.mp4?t=1743230903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Construct buildings on <strong>rooftops</strong> to save space and gain strategic advantages, like shooting over walls to defend against threats, making it easier to take down zombies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless zombie hordes push you to the limit.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/377f6c4137424d80b5f6e12c94835126.poster.avif?t=1743230903\" width=598 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/377f6c4137424d80b5f6e12c94835126.webm?t=1743230903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/377f6c4137424d80b5f6e12c94835126.mp4?t=1743230903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The zombie horde never stops. They are too many. <strong>Research, develop advanced technology, and train survivors</strong> to combat the ever-growing and evolving undead threat. Adapt or be overrun.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grow, manage, and protect your settlement</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/8bfc39e01c8f2aa0465a48df26dc5bd3.poster.avif?t=1743230903\" width=598 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/8bfc39e01c8f2aa0465a48df26dc5bd3.webm?t=1743230903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3543130/extras/8bfc39e01c8f2aa0465a48df26dc5bd3.mp4?t=1743230903\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Create a secure haven where survivors can <strong>eat, sleep, and recover</strong>. Establish a steady supply of food and resources, and build an efficient crafting chain to support your frontline fighters. </p>",
